    "path": "/blog/3",
    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<br>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"-준비\" style=\"position:relative;\">🗡 준비<a href=\"#-%EC%A4%80%EB%B9%84\" aria-label=\" 준비 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"(https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-plugin-sitemap#example)\"><strong>gatsby-plugin-sitemap</strong></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">sitemap.xml</code>   도메인 내의 <em>페이지 목록</em>을 명시한다.</li>\n<li>Bot들이 쉽게 사이트를 수집할 수 있도록 도와준다. 보이지 않는 페이지도 문제없이 크롤링되도록.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"(https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-plugin-robots-txt/)\"><strong>gatsby-plugin-robots-txt</strong></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">robots.txt</code> 생성해 준다.</li>\n<li>웹페이지를 수집할 수 있도록 허용하거나 제한한다. (관리자 페이지같이 보안이 필요한 부분을 제한)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> gatsby-plugin-sitemap gatsby-plugin-robots-txt</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  siteMetadata<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n    siteUrl<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://bepyan.github.io</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-sitemap</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-robots-txt</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>프로덕션 빌드하면 <code class=\"language-text\">/sitemap/sitemap-index.xml</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">/robots.txt</code> url로 접근이 가능하다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>참고로 구글에서는 sitemap의 changefreq, priority 필드를 무시하고 lastmod 필드를 본다고 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"-google-search-console\" style=\"position:relative;\">🗡 Google Search Console<a href=\"#-google-search-console\" aria-label=\" google search console permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://search.google.com/search-console/welcome?utm_source=about-page\">Google Search Console</a>에 등록할 수 있다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>도메인(DNS)에 등록하지 않았기에 우측 URL 접두어에 작성하자</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65283190/136661718-67b9ad83-5d3e-474e-a664-f384e2678d64.png\" alt=\"서치콘솔\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>HTML 태그를 통한 소유권을 확인\n<ul>\n<li>meta정보를 <code class=\"language-text\">SearchEngine.js</code>, Helmet 컴포넌트 안에 작성하면 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Helmet\n  //...\n  meta={[\n    {\n      name: \"google-site-verification\",\n      content: \"복사한 콘텐트\"\n    },\n    //...\n  ]}\n/></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>소유권 확인이 되면 Sitemaps가서 <code class=\"language-text\">/sitemap/sitemap-index.xml</code> 입력\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65283190/136669156-c45c61d9-427e-4f11-9888-2c0b4e47e221.png\" alt=\"image\">\n<ul>\n<li>만약 가져올 수 없다고하면 URL 검사 -> 색인 생성 요청하자.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>robots.txt 는 Google이 알아서 잘 크롤링 할 것이다.</li>\n<li>실제 사이트가 등록되기까지 시간이 걸리므로 몇일 후 시도해보도록 하자.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li>3일 후 sitemap이 색인되었다!\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65283190/137378661-bd6f04d7-2a8a-4c29-9135-2cd3e47cfc1a.png\" alt=\"image\"></li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"-naver-search-advisor\" style=\"position:relative;\">🗡 Naver Search Advisor<a href=\"#-naver-search-advisor\" aria-label=\" naver search advisor permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://searchadvisor.naver.com/console/board\">네이버 웹마스터</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>구글과 똑같이 진행하면된다. meta에 정보 입력하고 배포한 후 소유확인.</li>\n<li>웹마스터 도구 -> 사이트관리 -> 사이트 선택 -> 요청 -> 사이트맵 입력</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65283190/136664386-1d7cd06b-546e-4b50-ac8c-f1b542340bb3.png\" alt=\"네이버 사이트맵\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>검증 -> robots.txt -> 수집 요청</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65283190/136668861-6df8896d-4513-4ddb-b305-a329378a4908.png\" alt=\"robots 수집 요청\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>설정 -> 수집 주기 설정 -> 빠르게</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65283190/136669274-9628f458-fe87-4295-bff1-15ec3b6904b8.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>네이버도 마찬가지로 실제 사이트 등록되기까지 시간이 걸린다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"-daum-검색-등록\" style=\"position:relative;\">🗡 Daum 검색 등록<a href=\"#-daum-%EA%B2%80%EC%83%89-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\" aria-label=\" daum 검색 등록 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://register.search.daum.net/index.daum\">Daum 검색 등록</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>어려운 절차 없이 바로 등록 신청이 가능하다.</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#-%EC%A4%80%EB%B9%84\">🗡 준비</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#-google-search-console\">🗡 Google Search Console</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#-naver-search-advisor\">🗡 Naver Search Advisor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#-daum-%EA%B2%80%EC%83%89-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\">🗡 Daum 검색 등록</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"🗡 준비 gatsby-plugin-sitemap    도메인 내의 페이지 목록을 명시한다. Bot들이 쉽게 사이트를 수집할 수 있도록 도와준다. 보이지 않는 페이지도 문제없이 크롤링되도록. gatsby-plugin-robots-txt…","frontmatter":{"date":"2021-10-09","path":"/blog/3","title":"Gatsby 블로그 검색엔진 등록하기"},"fields":{"readingTime":{"text":"3 min read"}}}},"pageContext":{}},
